<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Warhammer Character Profile</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: #0a0a0a url('https://i.imgur.com/Yp1dM8y.png') no-repeat center/cover;
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      color: #e0d9c5;
    }

    .overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
      backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
    }

    .container {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 48px;
      text-align: center;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: #d6c287;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px #5a3e11;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #b09e74;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .profile-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .portrait {
      border: 3px solid #5b4a1e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px #3a2c0f;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(20, 20, 20, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid #5b4a1e;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .card h2 {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #5b4a1e;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #d6c287;
    }

    .data-table td {
      padding: 6px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px dashed #5b4a1e;
    }

    .timeline {
      border-left: 2px solid #5b4a1e;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .quote {
      font-style: italic;
      border-left: 4px solid #8c6a2b;
      padding-left: 10px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
      /* --- NEW WARHAMMER FX --- */
    /* Flickering holo text */
    @keyframes flicker {
      0% { opacity: 0.9; }
      50% { opacity: 0.65; }
      100% { opacity: 0.9; }
    }

    .title, .subtitle {
      animation: flicker 2.8s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Noise overlay */
    .noise-layer {
      pointer-events: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: url('https://i.imgur.com/5lH3KqJ.png');
      opacity: 0.07;
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
      animation: noiseMove 0.8s steps(4) infinite;
    }

    @keyframes noiseMove {
      0% {transform: translate(0,0);}  
      25% {transform: translate(20px,-10px);} 
      50% {transform: translate(-10px,10px);} 
      75% {transform: translate(-10px,-20px);} 
      100% {transform: translate(0,0);} 
    }

    /* Scanlines */
    .scanlines::before {
      content: "";
      pointer-events: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 2px,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 3px,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 6px
      );
      opacity: 0.3;
    }

    /* Glowing Borders */
    .card, .portrait {
      position: relative;
    }

    .card::after, .portrait::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border: 2px solid rgba(190, 160, 80, 0.25);
      filter: blur(3px);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    /* Slight holographic distortion */
    @keyframes distort {
      0% { transform: translate(0); } 
      50% { transform: translate(1px, -1px); } 
      100% { transform: translate(0); }
    }

    .portrait {
      animation: distort 2s infinite linear;
    }
      /* --- INQUISITION WARNING RUNES --- */
    @keyframes runeGlow {
      0% { opacity: 0.4; text-shadow: 0 0 4px #8b0000; }
      50% { opacity: 1; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ff1a1a; }
      100% { opacity: 0.4; text-shadow: 0 0 4px #8b0000; }
    }

    .warning-runes {
      position: fixed;
      top: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      color: #ff2a2a;
      font-size: 22px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      opacity: 0.85;
      animation: runeGlow 3s infinite ease-in-out;
      transform: rotate(8deg);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="scanlines" class="scanlines">
  <div class="noise-layer"></div>
  <div class="overlay"></div>
  <div class="warning-runes">⚠ LEX IMPERATORIS VIGILAT ⚠</div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="title">ИНКВИЗИТОР МАРКОС ВЕСТАН</div>
    <div class="subtitle">Ordo Malleus • Imperium of Man</div>

    <div class="profile-grid">

      <!-- Portrait -->
      <img class="portrait" src="https://i.imgur.com/EE1z6tY.jpeg" width="350" />

      <div class="details">
        <!-- Summary -->
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Краткая Сводка</h2>
          <table class="data-table" width="100%">
            <tr><td><b>Фракция</b></td><td>Империум</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Роль</b></td><td>Инквизитор Ордос Маллеус</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Планета</b></td><td>Гелиос-IX</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Статус</b></td><td>Активен</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <!-- Lore -->
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Лор-Описание</h2>
          Маркос Вестан — один из самых безжалостных охотников на демонов и культистов Хаоса. Его методы
          вызывают страх не только у врагов Империума, но и среди собственных союзников.
          <div class="quote">“Страх — это костыль. Вера — наше оружие.”</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Abilities -->
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Способности</h2>
          — Экзорцистический пси-импульс<br>
          — Молот Византария (артефактный вархаммер)<br>
          — Допрос в состоянии нейро-шторма<br>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Хронология</h2>
          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item"><b>743.M41</b> — вступление в Инквизицию</div>
            <div class="timeline-item"><b>748.M41</b> — раскрытие культа «Семя Кровавой Луны»</div>
            <div class="timeline-item"><b>755.M41</b> — сожжение планеты Лира-7</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
